section.title: Difference between Historical and Design Rainfall
section.para: An outline of the differences between historical storm events and design rainfall will be presented here. Important items to highlight will be the inconsistent frequency of historical rainfall, the differences between historical and design temporal patterns, and the differences in spatial patterns.
